  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 24px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" data-pm-slice=\"5 3 []\">\n   <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 10px 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div style=\"align-self:flex-start;padding:0px 24px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;display:inline-block;vertical-align:top;border-color:rgb(212, 32, 2) rgb(212, 32, 2) rgb(53, 175, 253);box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;max-width:100%;flex:0 0 auto;width:676.998px;border-width:0px 0px 2px;border-style:solid;\">\n     <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;text-align: justify;visibility: visible;\">\n      <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4255555555555556\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"900\" style=\"width:498px;height:212px;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/ibJzB4CZdSVXyXUOTsfic3WnK4Y4ZsS6o3qtl9dlibD46z0aug9onIsTUp5EmlhIu9CVNdYzozzUcqSe0bS2TntwA/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"498\" data-cropsely2=\"212\" data-imgfileid=\"503193022\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d5aeb1ed&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FibJzB4CZdSVXyXUOTsfic3WnK4Y4ZsS6o3qtl9dlibD46z0aug9onIsTUp5EmlhIu9CVNdYzozzUcqSe0bS2TntwA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      <p style=\"margin: 32px 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">对话嘉宾</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">造物时代创始人、CEO 张邱溪</span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">对话背景</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">不久前，造物时代旗下最新一代的桌面 CNC Makera Z1 拿下了千万美元的众筹成绩。千万美元，是 2025 年智能硬件获得市场认可的一个里程碑，如安克的 eufyMake E1、快造科技的 Snapmaker U1。同时，对于创客三件套（3D打印机、激光雕刻机、桌面 CNC）中的 CNC 来说，是有史以来的最好成绩。</span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">本次对话张邱溪，我们希望了解对于发展速度相对较慢的桌面 CNC 来说，本次众筹突破千万美元是否会成为 CNC 从服务小众到大众的转折点，CNC 又能否成为继 3D 打印之后中国品牌的一个强势赛道</span></span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);white-space-collapse:collapse;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, 